title: Hannah Jeter Is Pregnant
text: Hannah Jeter Just Announced Her Pregnancy in The Sweetest Way February 14, 2017 9:36 PM Photo: Getty Images D Dipasupil On Monday, in a loving Valentine's Day ode to her husband Derek Jeter on his website, The Players’ Tribune , Hannah Jeter snuck in a surprise pregnancy announcement. “Big moments also have a funny way of making you look ahead,” she wrote. “Now, pregnant with our first child, Derek and I are looking to the future.” In the post — which also includes a photo of the famous baseball player and now father-to-be holding a giant bunch of pink balloons — the model reveals that the baby is a girl. "He [Jeter] already has a name in mind — he’s set on it," she wrote. "Whatever her name is, I know she’ll run circles around him." This will be the first baby for the couple, who married in Napa last July. Recommended For You
